OL,3,C'Will learn from this': BAFTA launches
OL,4,Creview into racial slur at film awards
OL,6,FBAFTA bosses have told its members
OL,7,Fthat the organisation "will learn"
OL,8,Ffrom the shocking racial abuse which
OL,9,Fwas shouted out and broadcast during
OL,10,FSunday night's film awards ceremony.
OL,12,FIt said it took "full responsibility"
OL,13,Ffor putting guests and members in a
OL,14,F"very difficult situation".
OL,16,FTourette's campaigner John Davidson
OL,17,Fwas attending the awards ceremony
OL,18,Fafter inspiring the film, I Swear,
OL,19,Fwhich dramatises his life with severe
OL,20,FTourette syndrome.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
