OL,3,C'Will learn from this': BAFTA launches
OL,4,Creview into racial slur at film awards
OL,6,FIn a letter seen by ITV News, BAFTA
OL,7,Ftold members that a comprehensive
OL,8,Freview into what happened is underway
OL,9,Fand that they are taking this
OL,10,F"seriously".
OL,12,FThe BBC has also issued its own
OL,13,Fapology for the broadcast.
OL,15,FA senior BBC executive has apologised
OL,16,Fto staff, saying the corporation
OL,17,Funderstands "how distressing" it was
OL,18,Fthat the racial slur was not edited
OL,19,Fout.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
