OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771974352
OL,3,C'Will learn from this': BAFTA launches
OL,4,Creview into racial slur at film awards
OL,6,FIt's understood film studio Warner
OL,7,FBros is also believed to have raised
OL,8,Fimmediate concerns about the racial
OL,9,Fslur and requested it be removed from
OL,10,Fthe BBC broadcast.
OL,12,FIn a note sent to staff on Tuesday,
OL,13,Fseen by ITV News, the corporation's
OL,14,Fchief content officer Kate Phillips
OL,15,Fsaid the slur was "aired in error" and
OL,16,F"we would never have knowingly allowed
OL,17,Fthis to be broadcast."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
