OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771974352
OL,3,C'Will learn from this': BAFTA launches
OL,4,Creview into racial slur at film awards
OL,6,FThe note also said: "Award attendees
OL,7,Fwere pre-warned about the possibility
OL,8,Fof involuntary verbal tics associated
OL,9,Fwith Tourette Syndrome at the start of
OL,10,Fthe show, and Alan Cumming addressed
OL,11,Fit during the broadcast. Of course,
OL,12,Fthis doesn't lessen the impact and
OL,13,Fupset.
OL,15,F"The edit team removed another racial
OL,16,Fslur from the broadcast. This one was
OL,17,Faired in error and we would never have
OL,18,Fknowingly allowed this to be
OL,19,Fbroadcast."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
