OL,3,C'Will learn from this': BAFTA launches
OL,4,Creview into racial slur at film awards
OL,6,FOn Monday night, Davidson said he was
OL,7,F"deeply mortified if anyone considers
OL,8,Fmy involuntary tics to be intentional
OL,9,For to carry any meaning".
OL,11,FLabour MP Dawn Butler has accused the
OL,12,FBBC of "an obvious bias" and a
OL,13,F"failure of duty of care".
OL,15,FMeanwhile, film-maker Jonte Richardson
OL,16,Fhas said he is stepping down as a
OL,17,FBAFTA judge over the academy's
OL,18,Fhandling of the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
