OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1771974352
OL,3,C'Will learn from this': BAFTA launches
OL,4,Creview into racial slur at film awards
OL,6,FDuring the broadcast, the awards
OL,7,Fceremony's presenter Cumming
OL,8,Fapologised for the language viewers
OL,9,Fmay have heard.
OL,11,FDavidson was at the BAFTAs
OL,12,Frepresenting the film, I Swear, which
OL,13,Ftells the story of the Scottish
OL,14,Fcampaigner's life with the condition,
OL,15,Fwhich he developed when he was 12.
OL,17,FIt stars Robert Aramayo, who won best
OL,18,Factor for his performance in the film,
OL,19,Fwhich also won best casting. He was
OL,20,Falso named EE Rising Star.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
